{"tid":1047034,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企都係咁","createTime":"2019-03-04T16:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T14:29:14.000Z","uid":206363,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b4612d657c268d3af55cc998499a7d9e3c63aaef","tid":1047034,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:19:31.000Z","msg":"一返到去，屋企人都係黑口黑面<br />\n有時問下佢嘢：有冇見過我啲嘢 ，閪曬面話：無喎、唔知喎 <br />\n又或者分享下返學啲嘢，又會勁差態度咁答：哦、咁又點、係咩<br />\n同佢哋講嘢永遠都係閪口閪面，眼尾都唔望一下，佢哋長期燥底咁，明明都無嚟m。<br />\n阿媽係咁，阿妹又係咁，唔知點解好似前世得罪曬佢哋咁。<br />\n其實都係想返到去，有人可以傾下一兩句姐，我又唔係煩住佢哋。唉。"},{"pid":"4c9fe80aff814c5000c0fd66a8c21cf4d9ab3fed","tid":1047034,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"有無諗過你唔係佢地親生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06506580e0e69bd29c91ae64eefadd2b812b25f","tid":1047034,"uid":203983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c55a0e3fe3f3240533e04fab2b6fd2d7b1bcb9df","tid":1047034,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c9fe80aff814c5000c0fd66a8c21cf4d9ab3fed","tid":1047034,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"有無諗過你唔係佢地親生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係似樣㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af79e328517a181500c21d13828a36cb3e45522","tid":1047034,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c55a0e3fe3f3240533e04fab2b6fd2d7b1bcb9df","tid":1047034,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c9fe80aff814c5000c0fd66a8c21cf4d9ab3fed","tid":1047034,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"有無諗過你唔係佢地親生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=